Text:
It seems that this is just the evaluation version so only a little part of the browsers from the full package are available.

IMO this torrent is useless. You can dl the latest trial version directly from the dev website... :/

Well I tested somewhat further...

The trial time limit seems to be disabled so this can be useful but only a few standalone browsers are available (evaluation version).

Nonetheless you can make screenshots of many more browsers and compare them so this part at least seems to work like the licensed version.
